	<div id="about">
	<h1> ABOUT </h1>
		<p>CodeConnect.us is a online resource to connect experienced developers with aspiring students around the local Austin community. We believe that coding is an integral skill of the future and our aim is to provide easier access for students of all abilities, ages, and incomes.<br/>
		With CodeConnect.us, developers can make themselves available for volunteering sessions based on their customized availability and students can then browse the database of local developers to request booking sessions as needed. No sign-up fees required,
just a desire to code. Happy coding!</p>
	</div>

